properties.general_re: Some part of this plantation was done some months ago. It looks like the area is not cultivated.
Farmers cultivate two main types of fields on the said piece of land at different time intervals. In some cases you will see one or two oil palm in farm.
This section of field will in no time turn to cocoa farm.
The field is a mixed crop farm.

Most part of the cell is dominated by cocoa farming.Some years to come the entire cell will be cocoa farm because the remaining part of the cell is been used  for  plantain and cassava cultivation and the farmers have cocoa nursery ready for planting.
Their main crop farming is palm plantation because cocoa trees do not lust long or do not grow well on the land.
The interviewee works on the said piece of land for salary.
Cocoa grows very well within this section of the cell.
We can contact Mr. Dunstan Ayivie if the need be. His contact has been filled in space.
Cocoa do not lust long that is about 3 years and the trees started to whither.
The palm was the first to to be planted on this field.
